--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.1.0 (2017-08-26)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE

* Version 1.0.0 (2017-08-01)
I: Stabilize, improve and cleanup Ansible role

* Version 0.14.0 (2017-04-16)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.1
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.0

* Version 0.13.1 (2016-12-14)
I: Consolidate and improve redundant Ansible tasks

* Version 0.13.0 (2016-10-14)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE

* Version 0.12.0 (2016-09-03)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.0
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 5.9

* Version 0.11.1 (2016-05-29)
I: Improve FreeBSD support

* Version 0.11.0 (2016-05-21)
F: Add support for Ansible 2.0

* Version 0.10.1 (2016-04-15)
I: Improve 'all' 'group' and 'host' options

* Version 0.10.0 (2016-04-09)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.2-RELEASE

* Version 0.9.0 (2016-04-02)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 5.9
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 5.8

* Version 0.8.0 (2016-02-28)
F: Add support for OS family 'OpenBSD'

* Version 0.7.0 (2016-01-21)
F: Drop support for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.6.4 (2015-11-17)
I: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.6.3 (2015-11-08)
I: Improve 'group_vars' and 'host_vars' options

* Version 0.6.2 (2015-04-10)
B: Fix 'user_state' option

* Version 0.6.1 (2014-12-17)
I: Various small Ansible and Jinja2 improvements

* Version 0.6.0 (2014-12-04)
F: Add option to modify 'home'

* Version 0.5.1 (2014-09-11)
I: Change license from 'GPLv2' to 'Simplified BSD License'

* Version 0.5.0 (2014-08-28)
F: Add support for OS family 'FreeBSD'

* Version 0.4.0 (2014-08-14)
F: Remove support for OS family 'RedHat'

* Version 0.3.1 (2014-07-17)
B: Fix issue with 'authorized_key' when not defined

* Version 0.3.0 (2014-07-17)
F: Add support for 'default' and 'custom' user
I: Improve role dependencies

* Version 0.2.2 (2014-06-21)
B: Remove ansible variable directory
B: Correct mistake in documentation

* Version 0.2.1 (2014-05-25)
B: Fix 'group' option

* Version 0.2.0 (2014-05-25)
F: Add missing 'group' and 'groups' options

* Version 0.1.1 (2014-05-17)
B: Add missing 'shadow' dependency

* Version 0.1.0 (2014-05-14)
F: Initial release
